/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk18on/BCEdDSAPrivateKeyTest.java`\n\nKey changes:\n\n- Replaced provider-based `KeyPairGenerator.getInstance(\"Ed25519\", provider)` usage, which failed under Native Image because the provider service was unavailable.\n- Now instantiates Bouncy Castle’s public Ed25519 SPI directly via `KeyPairGeneratorSpi.Ed25519`.\n- Avoids full Java deserialization of the key object, which can fail under Native Image due unrelated serialization constructor reflection.\n- Invokes the serialization hooks with `MethodHandle`s and custom `ObjectInputStream` / `ObjectOutputStream` subclasses so execution reaches:\n  - `BCEdDSAPrivateKey.writeObject(...)`\n  - nested `ObjectOutputStream.writeObject(...)`\n  - `BCEdDSAPrivateKey.readObject(...)`\n  - nested `ObjectInputStream.readObject()`\n- Verifies the restored key state by comparing algorithm, format, encoding, hash code, equality, and public key encoding.\n\nI did not compile or run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fd4d91412df7b500169fbddfe30a0819f8f3ba12b6df9da92\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 524, "output": 788, "cacheRead": 38912, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 40224, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778114035666, "responseId": "resp_0fd4d91412df7b500169fbddf449f8819f8fd4d0e378e41546"}, "toolResults": []}
